  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play as a dog your way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become mankind’s best friend or worst nightmare! Befriend the people around you to get good stuff or just steal anything not locked down. Pick a path with dog skills to hone your dog and perfect the way you want to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/2fa93fe60dd0e9de577c8bc79cc7ee51.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/2fa93fe60dd0e9de577c8bc79cc7ee51.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/2fa93fe60dd0e9de577c8bc79cc7ee51.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive in a vast modern world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge, loot, and dig your way through life. Explore a world where the people and items are always changing. The city and its surroundings are yours to make your own!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/e218e8c610724246b240818782026b18.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/e218e8c610724246b240818782026b18.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/e218e8c610724246b240818782026b18.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trade for the Best Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need a quick snack? How about a weapon or some armor? This cat has it all but drives a hard bargain. Never fear! There is always room to negotiate. Sell special items, haggle, and do favors to get those prices right where you need them to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/99e284f8d82538067df2454bbddcf716.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/99e284f8d82538067df2454bbddcf716.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/99e284f8d82538067df2454bbddcf716.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deck out your penthouse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No dog should be without a home. And for you that means getting a badass apartment with the best stuff the city has to offer. Acquire amazing food, water, crafting options, and plenty more by expanding your apartment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/a0c4280423a7f2aff0e7e39079769b11.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/a0c4280423a7f2aff0e7e39079769b11.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/a0c4280423a7f2aff0e7e39079769b11.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the Mystery of Doggo City</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why are all the other pets missing, what happened to your human, and why do bad things keep happening to you? Work with a colorful cast of allies to uncover the mysteries of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take a trip to Ostrich Island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the serene beaches and palm trees of Ostrich Island, but don't let the tropical scenery fool you. Set up a safehouse, meet new characters, and take down the ultimate evil to all dog kind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
