ou? Work with a colorful cast of allies to uncover the mysteries of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/07979fc2c52881d2c2687de29141ebb3.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take a trip to Ostrich Island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the serene beaches and palm trees of Ostrich Island, but don't let the tropical scenery fool you. Set up a safehouse, meet new characters, and take down the ultimate evil to all dog kind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.poster.avif?t=1766779283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.webm?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027590/extras/fea2ce91d8885936308c9453ecc76e0c.mp4?t=1766779283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
